@startuml
title Part 1 — CI/CD Deployment Flow (GitHub Actions → Azure App Service)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica Neue"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam ArrowColor #34495E
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #34495E
  ParticipantBorderColor #2C3E50
  ParticipantFontColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontStyle bold
  ActorBackgroundColor #34495E
  ActorBorderColor #2C3E50
  LifeLineBorderColor #B0BEC5
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  GroupBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  GroupBorderColor #90A4AE
  GroupHeaderFontColor #2C3E50
  DividerBackgroundColor #34495E
  DividerFontColor #FFFFFF
}

actor Developer as Dev

box "GitHub" #ECEFF1
  participant Repo as "Repository\n(branch: main)"
  participant GHA as "GitHub Actions"
end box

box "Microsoft Azure" #E3F2FD
  participant UI as "App Service\np3-ui (React)"
  participant API as "App Service\np3-api (Spring Boot)"
end box

Dev -> Repo: 1. git push (main)
activate Repo
Repo -> GHA: 2. Trigger workflows (on: push / workflow_dispatch)
deactivate Repo
activate GHA

par Backend pipeline — main_erasmus-cc2025-api.yml
  GHA -> GHA: 3a. Setup Java 21 (microsoft)
  GHA -> GHA: 4a. mvn clean package -DskipTests
  GHA -> GHA: 5a. Rename fat JAR → app.jar + upload artifact
  GHA -> API: 6a. azure/login (secret: AZURE_CREDENTIALS)\nwebapps-deploy app.jar
  activate API
  API --> GHA: 7a. Deployed (Production slot)
  deactivate API
else Frontend pipeline — main_erasmus-cc2025-ui.yml
  GHA -> GHA: 3b. Setup Node.js 20.x
  GHA -> GHA: 4b. npm install
  GHA -> GHA: 5b. npm run build\n(REACT_APP_API_URL=https://p3-api.azurewebsites.net) → zip
  GHA -> UI: 6b. webapps-deploy node-release.zip\n(secret: AZURE_PUBLISHPROFILE)
  activate UI
  UI --> GHA: 7b. Deployed (Production slot)
  deactivate UI
end

GHA --> Dev: 8. Workflow status (success / failure)
deactivate GHA

note over UI, API
  Both services are reachable online afterwards:
  UI  → https://p3-ui.azurewebsites.net
  API → https://p3-api.azurewebsites.net
end note

@enduml
